{
  "texts": [
    "First of all, strings containing only element names were removed to focus on phase-property relationships rather than the effects of individual alloying elements.",
    "In this context, treating entities containing \"Si\" deserved special attention.",
    "In addition to \"Si\" as an element, \"Si\" also commonly refers to silicon as a phase.",
    "To isolate \"Si\" as a phase, we used the presence of the words \"eutectic,\" \"phase,\" or \"primary\" in the same sentence, which we found to be uniquely co-occurring with the silicon phase (but not Si element).",
    "Finally, we created a dictionary to map codified phase names into our selected unified notation."
  ]
}